=============================================================
Please note the following:

    - The system-wide procmailrc is expected in @PREFIX@/etc
      (e.g. @PREFIX@/etc/procmailrc).

    - The system-wide procmailrc directory is expected in
      @PREFIX@/etc (e.g. @PREFIX@/etc/procmailrcs/*).

=============================================================
